17. Bayelsa House.” The statement read. According to the statement, the FCT Commissioner of Police CP Babaji Sunday PSC has expressed confidence in the revamped security architecture in the FCT, and urged members of the public to cooperate with the Police and consider the use of alternative routes. He also noted that the arrangement was emplaced for security optimization and ease of transportation. YOU SHOULD NOT MISS THESE HEADLINES FROM NIGERIAN TRIBUNE We Have Not Had Water Supply In Months ― Abeokuta Residents In spite of the huge investment in the water sector by the government and international organisations, water scarcity has grown to become a perennial nightmare for residents of Abeokuta, the Ogun State capital. This report x-rays the lives and experiences of residents in getting clean, potable and affordable water amidst the surge of COVID-19 cases in the state… FCT Police deploy personnel  FCT Police deploy personnel Selfies, video calls and Chinese documentaries: The things you’ll meet onboard Lagos-Ibadan train The Lagos-Ibadan railway was inaugurated recently for a full paid operation by the Nigerian Railway Corporation after about a year of free test-run. Our reporter joined the train to and fro Lagos from Ibadan and tells his experience in this report… FCT Police deploy personnel  FCT Police deploy personnel ORITAMEFA BAPTIST MODEL SCHOOLS, (OBMS), IBADAN 
